5.Run a container named alpine-2 using the alpine image and attach it to the none network.

root@docker-host ~ ➜  docker container run --name alpine-2 --network=none alpine

6.Create a new network named wp-mysql-network using the bridge driver. Allocate subnet as 182.18.0.0/24 and configure gateway as 182.18.0.1.

root@docker-host ~ ➜  docker network create --driver bridge --subnet 182.18.0.0/24 --gateway 182.18.0.1 wp-mysql-network
