7.Deploy a mysql database using the mysql:8.4 image and name it mysql-db. Attach it to the newly created network wp-mysql-network.
Set the database password to db_pass123 using the MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD environment variable.

root@docker-host ~ ➜  docker container run -d -e MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=db_pass123 --name mysql-db --network wp-mysql-network mysql:8.4
